claim.claim-text:
12. An axle for use in a vehicle drive train, the drive train including a prop shaft having a pinion shaft connected thereto, said axle comprising: 
an axle housing; 
a differential housing rotatably supported within said axle housing; 
a ring gear attached to said differential housing, said ring gear engaging the pinion shaft; 
a differential gear set rotatably supported within said differential housing; 
a shaft engaging said differential gear set; and 
a reduction gear adjacent to said differential housing and a second gear, said second gear surrounding said shaft.

20. A differential for use in a vehicle, said differential including: 
a housing; 
a ring gear connected to an outside surface of said housing; 
a differential gear set rotatably supported within said housing; 
a differential pin connected to said differential gear set; 
a sun gear adjacent to said housing and said differential gear set said sun gear having a shift mechanism contacting one end thereof; 
a reduction gear engaging said sun gear; 
a hollow gear adjacent to an inside surface of said housing, said hollow gear engaging said reduction gear; 
a planet pin contacting said reduction gear; and 
a planet gear carrier engaging said planet pin.
